data.description: Welcome to a charming and hassle-free lifestyle in Newport's lovely community, where the absence of HOA fees enhances the appeal of this property. Just a few blocks away from Newport's prime amenities, including shopping, restaurants, parks, and the scenic Nye Beach, this residence offers both convenience and leisure. The recently updated appliances, featuring a washer and dryer, refrigerator, and range/oven, add a modern touch to the home. Enjoy glimpses of the ocean from the upstairs deck, providing a tranquil retreat. The shared community street has undergone recent improvements with repaved surfaces, and the city plumbing and electric have been updated. With a roof replacement less than 2 years ago, this property is not only a great investment opportunity but also an ideal choice for a second home or full-time living, combining practicality and comfort seamlessly.
